          <p class="lead">Australia offers world-renowned universities, innovative research opportunities, and a high quality of life. With its multicultural society, stunning landscapes, and excellent career prospects, it's an ideal destination for international students seeking a top-tier education in the Southern Hemisphere.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="col-lg-6">
          <img src="/user-assets/img/destinations/australiaOverview.cms" alt="Australia Overview" class="img-fluid rounded">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Key Facts Section -->
