        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Education System</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Australia's education system is known for its high standards, innovative teaching methods, and strong focus on research, with many universities ranking among the world's top institutions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Language</h5>
              <p class="card-text">English is the primary language of instruction in Australian universities, making it an excellent destination for international students to improve their English skills while studying.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4 mb-4">
          <div class="card h-100">
            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">Quality of Life</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Australia consistently ranks high in quality of life indices, offering students a safe, multicultural environment with excellent healthcare, diverse cuisine, and numerous recreational activities.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Top Universities Section -->
  <section class="py-5">
    <div class="container">
