            <div class="card-body">
              <h5 class="card-title">University of Sydney</h5>
              <p class="card-text">Australia's first university, renowned for its cutting-edge research and diverse student community.</p>
              <a href="https://www.sydney.edu.au/" class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank">Learn More</a>
